exceptions.tactic: intros w this l s H.
intros w' this l s H.
intros w' this' l s H.
intros w' this' l' s H.
intros w' this' l' s'' H.

original: intros w this l s H. unfold dom in H. rewrite getLocal in H. rewrite getStatelet. simpl. destruct (find l s) as [dstatelet|] eqn:Heq. - intros H0. reflexivity. - intros H0. inversion H0.
